title: OnceTest
---
<<set $gold_amount to 21.0>>
<<once>>
Player: I'd like to buy a pie!

<<if $gold_amount < 10>>
    Baker: Well, you can't afford one!
<<elseif $gold_amount < 15>>
    Baker: You can almost afford one!
<<else>>
    Baker: You can afford a pie!
<<endif>>

<<if $gold_amount + 1 > 11 + 2>>
    Baker: 1
<<elseif $gold_amount > 15>>
    Baker: 2
<<endif>>
<<endonce>>
and that was my adventure in town!
===
